body:
@kolien , I changed my setup to use the Cloudant database in Bluemix and I'm able to replicate this issue.  I only see changes when the write is issued from the CLI.  I am unable to see changes when I use the Cloudant dashboard.  @rabbah I suppose this is a bug -- perhaps because Bluemix setups have to go thru the Bluemix Cloudant broker?

If you would like to use the Cloudant dashboard, I recommend setting up the Cloudant database outside of Bluemix as a workaround. That works for me.

Thanks for finding this!
